            "notes": "The deck revolves around utilizing various spells and abilities to control the game and disrupt the opponent's strategy while also generating card advantage. It focuses on efficiently countering threats, bouncing opposing permanents, and digging for key cards with cantrips and tutors. The commander, Lier, Disciple of the Drowned, synergizes well with the deck by allowing for spell recursion and providing additional value from casting instants and sorceries from the graveyard. The goal is to out tempo the opponent and maintain board control through a combination of disruption and card advantage, ultimately overwhelming them with a steady stream of threats and powerful spells."
